            <abstract>
                <p>A short hymn referring to <ref type="work" corresp="LIT3588Miracle"/>, which it may follow in manuscripts containing the
                    <ref type="work" corresp="LIT2384Taamme"/>. It seems to be part of a larger collection of hymns following particular miracles, 
                    as attested in <ref type="mss" corresp="ESmac001"/>.
                </p>
